+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js v24.18.0
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- implementation: data
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: none
+- scantlings: scantlings
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run --format progress --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- focused: `bash -c 'ref="$0"; npx cucumber-js --name "${ref##*:}" --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"' {scenario}`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --format progress --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --reporter=text npx cucumber-js --format progress --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- plank-inventory: `npx jsdoc -X src/tide.js`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: `npx biome lint src/`
+- conformance: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright and @conformance"`
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic uses local data only, no external services
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber@13.2.0
+- dependency: c8@12.0.0
+- dependency: @biomejs/biome@2.5.5
+- dependency: jsdoc@4.0.5
+- dependency: knip@6.29.0
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
